    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >感谢的所有&quot;氪佬&quot;对《中国式网游》的喜爱和支持，我们决定免费推出DLC送给所有玩家！<br>预告：下一个DLC将会是&quot;彩票模式&quot;也会免费送给大家！</h2><br>&quot;爽文&quot;模式DLC新内容汇总如下：<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >新增系统：</h2>一、坐骑系统<br>玩家可以在游戏商城中购买约8种不同外观的坐骑，提升战斗力。<br>二、新宝石抽奖系统<br>全新的氪金系统，可以结局玩家宝石产出少的问题。<br>三、超级技能玩法<br>内丹系统，升级战斗力。<br>四、帮派建设玩法<br>玩家可以通过购买帮派基础建设提升战斗力。<br>五、天命人隐藏系统<br>根据剧情推进，玩家找到3个彩蛋将会获得究极大奖。<br>六、美女客服系统<br>美女客服将会引导&quot;天命&quot;玩家继续&quot;氪&quot;金。<br>七、红颜系统<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193590/extras/7a62f97dcf32cbbea97dbed61cfb4153.avif?t=1727405653\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193590/extras_big/7a62f97dcf32cbbea97dbed61cfb4153.avif?t=1727405653 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193590/extras/88c8e14ee278b1486547f5833a89be07.avif?t=1727405653\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193590/extras_big/88c8e14ee278b1486547f5833a89be07.avif?t=1727405653 width=800 height=450 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >变动以及优化：</h2>一、老王的新房以及换装系统<br>在地图中新增老王的豪宅，可在房间内替换老王的服装。<br>二、100连抽<br>在&quot;爽文&quot;模式中，玩家的抽奖最高提提高至100连抽。<br>三、地图扩建<br>在地图中新增“高端商场“、&quot;豪宅&quot;板块。<br>四、AI系统优化<br>在&quot;爽文&quot;模式下,AI言行举止将会客气许多。<br>五、无尽模式<br>很多玩家反馈，当上城主后不能继续游玩了，在爽文模式下，当上城主可以继续游玩。<br>六、老王情绪更稳定<br>老王在变有钱后，心情会持续保持稳定，基本不会崩溃。<br>七、公司系统更改<br>老王在变有钱后，将不需要去公司上班。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193590/extras/e1336ac1750b57e60c1aa5ad83c921ff.avif?t=1727405653\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193590/extras_big/e1336ac1750b57e60c1aa5ad83c921ff.avif?t=1727405653 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193590/extras/2d97ef1e3558bdbbde70d3233f25be9d.avif?t=1727405653\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193590/extras_big/2d97ef1e3558bdbbde70d3233f25be9d.avif?t=1727405653 width=800 height=450 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >新增专属结局动画：</h2>一、专属结局<br>在&quot;爽文&quot;模式中，将会新增2个结局动画<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193590/extras/5d52271f01738aa1b82f65890ad2c9f0.avif?t=1727405653\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193590/extras_big/5d52271f01738aa1b82f65890ad2c9f0.avif?t=1727405653 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><br>最后非常感谢大家的等待，DLC推出不代表游戏停止更新，我们还会持续优化问题，认真听取玩家的反馈更新新内容。",
